        "syns": [
            {
                "pl": "synonyms",
                "pt": [
                    [
                        "text",
                        "{sc}civil{/sc} {sc}polite{/sc} {sc}courteous{/sc} {sc}gallant{/sc} {sc}chivalrous{/sc} mean observant of the forms required by good breeding. {sc}civil{/sc} often suggests little more than the avoidance of overt rudeness. "
                    ],
                    [
                        "vis",
                        [
                            {
                                "t": "owed the questioner a {it}civil{/it} reply"
                            }
                        ]
                    ],
                    [
                        "text",
                        " {sc}polite{/sc} commonly implies polish of speech and manners and sometimes suggests an absence of cordiality. "
                    ],
                    [
                        "vis",
                        [
                            {
                                "t": "if you can't be pleasant, at least be {it}polite{/it}"
                            }
                        ]
                    ],
                    [
                        "text",
                        " {sc}courteous{/sc} implies more actively considerate or dignified politeness. "
                    ],
                    [
                        "vis",
                        [
                            {
                                "t": "clerks who were unfailingly {it}courteous{/it} to customers"
                            }
                        ]
                    ],
                    [
                        "text",
                        " {sc}gallant{/sc} and {sc}chivalrous{/sc} imply courteous attentiveness especially to women. {sc}gallant{/sc} suggests spirited and dashing behavior and ornate expressions of courtesy. "
                    ],
                    [
                        "vis",
                        [
                            {
                                "t": "a {it}gallant{/it} suitor of the old school"
                            }
                        ]
                    ],
                    [
                        "text",
                        " {sc}chivalrous{/sc} suggests high-minded and self-sacrificing behavior. "
                    ],
                    [
                        "vis",
                        [
                            {
                                "t": "a {it}chivalrous{/it} display of duty"
                            }
                        ]
                    ]
                ]
            }
        ],
        "et": [
            [
                "text",
